modules/gitorious - Puppet recipe for install Gitorious (www.gitorious.com) on a CentOS 5.3/5.4 machine.
  Prerequisites: rubygems, puppet 0.25.1
    1. Install EPEL repo
    2. yum -y install rubygems; gem install --no-ri --no-rdoc facter puppet
  Usage instructions:
    1. clone the repo into /etc/puppet/
    2. Run `puppet /etc/puppet/sites.pp`
    3. Open http://yourserver.yourdomain/
